reviewText: My kids ages 2-11 all love these songs

This dvd is amazing... i use it for kids church and they love to dance and sing and worship god..  also we use some songs for youth and they really enjoy it...if u don't have a kids band or youth band this will help u with worship...
wonderful children's praise music- Perfect for ages 4-8 in my opinion!
excellent for our church's Kids Ministry!
Fast shipping, product as described, highly recommend seller. Disappointed. Great songs but video is nothing but words with psychedelic background.

Our kids LOVE these songs! The DVD is a great addition, especially because it's only a little more. The graphics are fun, but not distracting. The upbeat songs are a blast and the slower ones are great too! Overall VERY happy with the purchase!
Not at all what I expected.  Very disappointed.
Thank you for the fast delivery of my purchased items.  I will enjoy it.  I enjoy the songs as well as the moving backgrounds.  My kids choir love it too.
